org.bukkit.entity

Interface Entity

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Animals, Arrow, Boat, CaveSpider, Chicken, Cow, Creature, Creeper, Egg, Enderman, ExperienceOrb, Explosive, FallingSand, Fireball, Fish, Flying, Ghast, Giant, HumanEntity, Item, LightningStrike, LivingEntity, Minecart, Monster, Painting, Pig, PigZombie, Player, PoweredMinecart, Projectile, Sheep, Silverfish, Skeleton, Slime, Snowball, Spider, Squid, StorageMinecart, TNTPrimed, Vehicle, WaterMob, Weather, Wolf, Zombie

    public interface Entity
    Represents a base entity in the world
